dc_title_s: Kharitat khutut al-bas fi Baghdad wa dawahiha.
dc_description_s: Iraq. Mudiriyat Maslahat Naql al-Rukab al-'Ammah. Iraq. Directorate General of Passanger Transportation Service. Title translation: [Map of bus lines in Baghdad and its suburbs]. Relief is shown by hachures. Scale is stated on map as 1:20,000. However, the graphic and map scale is 1:33,330. Verso: Khutut al-basat fi Baghdad. [Bus routes of Baghdad}are located, Routes length is given.
